## Terms filter

The Terms filter is used to filter posts by taxonomy term(s). For example, categories, tags, and any custom taxonomies that you create.

It uses as a source a [Taxonomy field](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_taxonomy-field_.md)

## Options

- Label
- Placeholder
- Key
- Data source: Shows available taxonomies added to that CPT
- Term order:

1\. Default order

2\. Alphabetical
- Allow selection of multiple terms
- Search behaviour:

1\. Match posts containing ANY of the selected terms

2\. Match posts containing ALL of the selected terms
- Icon

## Default values

This filter expects one or multiple slugs as default value. If multiple, they have to be separated by commas.
